author: Silvia Amaro
title: Italy's coronavirus death toll is more than double that of China's — this might be why
description: Demographics, social behavior and lower testing capacity are just some of the reasons why Italy and Spain have the highest number of deaths from the coronavirus, health experts told CNBC.
